Class SDIAdapter

java.lang.Object
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.SclElementAdapter<SclElementAdapter,TSDI>
org.lfenergy.compas.sct.commons.scl.ied.SDIAdapter
All Implemented Interfaces:
IDataAdapter, IDataParentAdapter
public class SDIAdapter extends SclElementAdapter<SclElementAdapter,TSDI> implements IDataParentAdapter
A representation of the model object DOIAdapter.

The following features are supported:

  1. Adapter
    • Returns the value of the Child Adapter object reference
    • Returns the value of the Child Adapter object reference By Name
  2. Principal functions
    • Add TDAI under this object
    • Add TSDI under this object
    • Add TPrivate under this object
